{"tid":426354,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"M記食家 留低一個令食M記更好味的方法","createTime":"2017-10-06T14:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T06:54:41.000Z","uid":137997,"like":16,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"b064fa420b7a9c312522dc4ff5785c3d6d280cf5","tid":426354,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:05:47.000Z","msg":"食包要叫多醬 沙律醬 千島醬 一定要加 其他味自己選擇<br />\n<br />\n薯條要走鹽 通常會重炸 所以會熱啲好食啲脆啲 仲要加泰式辣醬 <br />\n<br />\n飲野要走冰 因為冰會溶 特別係埋尾幾口 越飲越淡越難飲 同埋通常杯冰佔左大半個杯 仲要唔知係咪乾淨 <br />\n所以走左冰 飲多啲好飲啲肚柯機會都小啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後最後最後</span></span><br />\n<br />\n做撚死班仆街就岩 安格斯出果陣明明有多醬 而家無左 <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請出招各位"},{"pid":"88c033f97faca93ca0142c55204b8d851c348157","tid":426354,"uid":4679,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"糖加茄汁"},{"pid":"d64715a8bec0f8f26c2edf8778094b3e112e5cec","tid":426354,"uid":116530,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"唱著歌嚟嗌餐"},{"pid":"bab911c47d90db163eb38d5581d7c006d618b65b","tid":426354,"uid":10699,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唱著歌嚟嗌餐</blockquote><br />\n唔好post條link 出來唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保你大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c577e4da3f2f6ef51b68a5a855b8b607d8cb4db","tid":426354,"uid":10427,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:15:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我～想～要</span></span>"},{"pid":"a5128b4ffe9dd6d4f31616032e3ce2b7f3b48407","tid":426354,"uid":134437,"like":1,"d