ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T00:23:18.000Z","msg":"食早餐 薯餅加茄汁先係王道"},{"pid":"330eb4d099d5cbfb28a99c49f89c2eced38f24c3","tid":426354,"uid":61075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T00:44:15.000Z","msg":"我～想～要～"},{"pid":"a7667e1a901657753522ad3c6962d66b26c0fdda","tid":426354,"uid":58086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食早餐 薯餅加茄汁先係王道</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  加jam 先係王道"},{"pid":"7b518a9bf15c7cc805ae74a5231f984d3bd41c1d","tid":426354,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:26:51.000Z","msg":"負皮既係M記員工?"},{"pid":"182900dd30b20ab5216ffa39b2177f708343cdbf","tid":426354,"uid":115140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:37:55.000Z","msg":"點解樓主咁中意食狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f4f821a986b178d4282e4becf747869e7445f0","tid":426354,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食早餐 薯餅加茄汁先係王道</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  加jam 先係王道</blockquote><br />\n<br />\njam太&quot;傑&quot; 茄汁濕濕地<br />\n易入口好多 同埋有少少酸味 好開胃"},{"pid":"7a21bd54affe2ae980f552732483950ebec9337f","tid":426354,"uid":91585,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"回應樓主<br />\n忙果陣特製都係亂咁出比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你叫走鹽其實可能仲唔新鮮<br />\n發夢果陣就教人炸定一籃擺係則邊專比你依啲傻仔食既<br />\n要叫就叫即炸，咁佢先會炸比你<br />\n汽水一定係有冰好飲過冇冰<br />\n為咗貪多果少少證明你係貪心<br />\n唔係證明你識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果咁你識食既你可以學啲廢老咁早餐叫一杯奶茶添十杯<br />\n唔係講笑，今朝條八婆已經添咗第十三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c383456a31bc920483731bdf71544b1f1d0350dc","tid":426354,"uid":58748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d4bf116c501dfba7c5147d1e9fcc38388e7d38d","tid":426354,"uid":93533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:15:50.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n野飲走冰 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013a2becf2d4f5ad62ced514da1b367575ae92d3","tid":426354,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"粟米 要問佢拎牛油"},{"pid":"695f95a5b38401e371b5b53c4ab8f7a232486f38","tid":426354,"uid":76005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>回應樓主<br />\n忙果陣特製都係亂咁出比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你叫走鹽其實可能仲唔新鮮<br />\n發夢果陣就教人炸定一籃擺係則邊專比你依啲傻仔食既<br />\n要叫就叫即炸，咁佢先會炸比你<br />\n汽水一定係有冰好飲過冇冰<br />\n為咗貪多果少少證明你係貪心<br />\n唔係證明你識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果咁你識食既你可以學啲廢老咁早餐叫一杯奶茶添十杯<br />\n唔係講笑，今朝條八婆已經添咗第十三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來可以叫即炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n包都可叫佢即製  但通常比人黑面<br />\n叫暑條前可以望下佢係咪炸定 '浪'起<br />\n有就都係暖暖地 呢啲情況我通常轉粟米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7a2de0b461a996e20e46cc75ad54b7e1800b16","tid":426354,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>回應樓主<br />\n忙果陣特製都係亂咁出比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你叫走鹽其實可能仲唔新鮮<br />\n發夢果陣就教人炸定一籃擺係則邊專比你依啲傻仔食既<br />\n要叫就叫即炸，咁佢先會炸比你<br />\n汽水一定係有冰好飲過冇冰<br />\n為咗貪多果少少證明你係貪心<br />\n唔係證明你識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果咁你識食既你可以學啲廢老咁早餐叫一杯奶茶添十杯<br />\n唔係講笑，今朝條八婆已經添咗第十三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來可